    <Paragraph Style="{StaticResource mainContentStyle}">
      <Bold>Panels</Bold> are components that control the rendering of elements—their size and dimensions, their position, and the arrangement of their child content. Rendering is controlled by properties specified on panels.
    </Paragraph>

